Welcome to the Ultanium Appcelerator Titanium Mobile Package

Ultanium is an attempt to bring the web 'Ultimate Package' to Titanium Mobile. 

It offers an out of the box best practice set up that: 

- Protects global namespace through self calling functions
- Uses MVC style helpers to create all common UI elements with JSS ID & Classes
- Allows for customised Apple iOS & Android compatible UIs through simple JSS
- Mixes in HTML5/CSS3 webviews to allow quick and easy to content management

The objective of Ultanium is provide a re-usable package which enables a quick 
start to create simple, native, information based mobile applications that can 
be easily branded through JSS and HTML/CSS.
